<section class="banner description">
    <div class="container inner">
        <h1>{{ title }}</h1>
        <p>Première fonctionnalité du site permettant d'importer des données au format CSV jusqu'à 1.000.000+ lignes en gardant un bon niveau de performances.<br/><i>Tech. EF6, BulkCopy, AngularJS</i></p>
    </div>
</section>

<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-7">

            <form>
                <div class="form-group input-group">
                    <span class="input-group-addon"><i class="fa fa-file green"></i></span>
                    <select class="form-control" name="species" role="combobox" data-ng-model="model.SpeciesId">
                        <option label="Maize" value="1"></option>
                        <option label="Barley" value="2"></option>
                        <option label="Durum Wheat" value="3"></option>
                        <option label="Common Wheat" value="4"></option>
                    </select>
                </div>


                <div class="form-group input-group">
                    <span class="input-group-addon"><i class="fa fa-file green"></i></span>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Harvest year..." data-ng-model="model.YearId">
                </div>

                <div class="form-group input-group">
                    <span class="input-group-addon"><i class="fa fa-file green"></i></span>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Campaign..." data-ng-model="model.CampaignId">
                </div>

                <div class="form-group input-group">
                    <span class="input-group-addon"><i class="fa fa-file green"></i></span>
                    <input type="date" class="form-control" placeholder="Publication date..." data-ng-model="model.PublicationDate">
                </div>

                <div class="form-group input-group">
                    <span class="input-group-addon"><i class="fa fa-file green"></i></span>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Source..." data-ng-model="model.SourceId">
                </div>

                <div class="form-group input-group">
                    <span class="input-group-addon"><i class="fa fa-building-o green"></i></span>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Variable..." data-ng-model="model.VariableId">
                </div>

                <div class="form-group input-group">
                    <span class="input-group-addon"><i class="fa fa-building-o green"></i></span>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Unit..." data-ng-model="model.UnitId">
                </div>

                <div class="form-group input-group">
                    <span class="input-group-btn">
                        <span class="btn btn-file btn-primary bg-green" data-ng-file-select ng-model="file" data-updloader="uploader">Browse...</span>
                    </span>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" readonly="" data-ng-model="model.SelectedFilename">
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <input class="btn btn-primary pull-right bg-green" type="submit" value="Upload" data-ng-click="upload()" />
                </div>
            </form>

        </div>

        <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-3 col-md-offset-1">
            <div class="info-zone bg-info">
                <h3>Need help?</h3>
                <p>
                    <span>Ut fusce varius nisl ac ipsum gravida vel pretium tellus tincidunt integer eu augue augue nunc elit dolor, luctus placerat.</span>
                    <span>Scelerisque euismod, iaculis eu lacus nunc mi elit, vehicula ut laoreet ac, aliquam sit amet justo nunc tempor, metus vel.</span>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>